>\n<br />\n後期自已留左2仔2女 其餘賣左出去<br />\n依家分兩個大膠箱3仔3女咁養<br />\n啲仔女都大哂lu 差唔多半歲<br />\n同老豆老母一樣肥斯大隻<br />\n大食到仆街 <br />\n$70 2lb mazuri 大鼠糧<br />\n一星期ko"},{"pid":"01aad8e724b6ce8633cdfb196d0c046918e15b16","tid":448284,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T18:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>花枝 鼠<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-iNkK__-AiKE/TodfyOzyeSI/AAAAAAAACGs/peC7RF3XnNE/s1600/squrat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-iNkK__-AiKE%2FTodfyOzyeSI%2FAAAAAAAACGs%2FpeC7RF3XnNE%2Fs1600%2Fsqurat.jpg&h=6ea9bb46&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8b66e74d8e81cb77d209891f452a93c07be55c","tid":448284,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T18:49:03.000Z","msg":"幾多年命"},{"pid":"6d8014af392b91c2f834959c45b3ce5836a9b190","tid":448284,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T18:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6隻 3仔3女<br />\n有象耳有立耳 <br />\n有直毛有單卷<br />\n乖到仆街 肥到仆街<br />\n一直覺得花枝先係鼠類入面最適合做寵物既鼠</blockquote><br />\n好想領養一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef026c54a1c35377045dc5f8004b5c4dc48cc23","tid":448284,"uid":100362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T19:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾多年命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n養得好 又唔近親繁殖既 4年"},{"pid":"01ce80712418e85c6337c3b11fa37f26a6eaee32","tid":448284,"uid":100362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T19:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6隻 3仔3女<br />\n有象耳有立耳 <br />\n有直毛有單卷<br />\n乖到仆街 肥到仆街<br />\n一直覺得花枝先係鼠類入面最適合做寵物既鼠</blockquote><br />\n好想領養一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj